data.name: sqlDataSource_Prepaid.SelectCommand
data.value: Select s.AirwayBillNo, cl.FirstName + ' '+' '+ cl.LastName, ptype.PaymentTypeName, s.TotalAmount,p.Amount, p.TaxWithheld, p.OrNo, p.PrNo, stat.PaymentSummaryName, validated.FirstName + ' '+validated.LastName, psummary.[Signature] from Payment p left join PaymentSummary psummary on p.PaymentId = psummary.PaymentId left join PaymentSummaryStatus stat on psummary.PaymentSummaryStatusId = stat.PaymentSummaryStatusId left join Shipment s on p.ShipmentId = s.ShipmentId left join Client cl on s.ConsigneeId = cl.ClientId left join PaymentMode pm on s.PaymentModeId = pm.PaymentModeId left join PaymentType ptype on p.PaymentTypeId = ptype.PaymentTypeId left join Employee emp on p.ReceivedById = emp.EmployeeId left join Employee validated on psummary.ValidatedBy = validated.EmployeeId left join RevenueUnit ru on emp.AssignedToAreaId = ru.RevenueUnitId left join RevenueUnitType rut on ru.RevenueUnitTypeId = rut.RevenueUnitTypeId left join City c on ru.CityId = c.CityId left join BranchCorpOffice bco on c.BranchCorpOfficeId = bco.BranchCorpOfficeId where pm.PaymentModeCode = 'PP' and stat.PaymentSummaryName = 'Validated' and psummary.[Signature] is not null and cast (PaymentDate as date) = '2017-02-16';
